Over the past **two weeks**, we've been working hard on improving the **security of the subnet**.

• **Activation function**  
• **Network architecture**  
• Whether **SDE** is used

Any model missing this file will **not be accepted or evaluated**.

---

**🧰 How to generate the JSON file?**

``RL.train_RL_with_info``

This script includes a function:  
``information_save(model)``  
Simply call it after training to generate the required `safe_policy_meta.json`

You can:
• **Retrain your model** using the new script  
• Or run `information_save()` on an **already trained model** to generate the file retroactively

This ensures only **valid**, **well-structured models** are rewarded while we stabilize the rollout.
